data.description: Cute 3 bedroom 2 bath northside Dinuba home. Semi-open concept, with a nice fireplace in the living room.  Laundry room is located indoors for your convenience. The backyard includes a small covered patio. There is also some custom flatwork.  Located in a cul-de-sac near elementary and middle schools.  Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity, schedule your appointment today!
